      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Chatbot: Hello! I am your AI assistant. Type 'exit' to end the chat.\n",
            "You: hello \n",
            "Chatbot: Hello! How can I assist you today? Is there something specific you'd like to know or talk about that isn't being asked for in this conversation?\n",
            "\n",
            "Please let me know if you have any questions. That way we can continue our interaction effectively. Have an amazing day! 😊😊✨\n",
            "\n",
            "Feel free to ask anything, whether it's personal advice, information on a topic of interest, or just curious thoughts. The more details you provide, the better equipped I will be at helping you with your queries.\n",
            "\n",
